milestones.description: Viswanath has scored 2 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for IND breaking Ajit Wadekar's record
Clive Lloyd has broken the record for most catches (7) in ODIs for WI, going past Holder's 6
Viv Richards has become the top scorer for WI in ODIs with 385 runs, going past Alvin Kallicharran's 378
Viswanath has become the top scorer for IND in ODIs with 223 runs, going past Brijesh Patel's 180
Srinivas Venkataraghavan has broken the record for most ODIs (5) as captain for IND, going past Bishan Bedi
Deryck Murray has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (13) for WI, going past Fredericks
Srinivas Venkataraghavan has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (10) for IND, going past Viswanath
Greenidge and Haynes's 138-run partnership is WI's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 52 between Deryck Murray and Fredericks
Viswanath and Kapil Dev's 35-run partnership is IND's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 19 between Viswanath and Brijesh Patel
Viswanath and Karsan Ghavri's 36-run partnership is IND's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 18 between Madan Lal and Brijesh Patel
Srinivas Venkataraghavan and Bishan Bedi's 27-run partnership is IND's highest for the 10th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 17 between Bhagwath Chandrasekhar and Pochiah Krishnamurthy
